name: Dandelion
description: i am single and never been married. i have no kids . i like to write stories, watch movies, football and baseball on tv. my fave colors are red, black and blue. my fave foods are pasta, chicken and seafood. i go to church and i am a christian. I’m looking for a serious relationship that will lead to marriage. I’m looking for a loving, caring, honest, trusting, truthful, sincere, sensitive man. I am loving, caring, honest, trusting. I do go to church whenever i can. I will not send money so dont ask. i dont want to talk to any military guys. because most of them on here are fake ones anyway. i only want to find someone who will love me for the rest of my life and be there when i need them for comfort or support. i want to get married and be happy. If you are between the ages of 25-40 check out my profile and lets see if we can be friends and then see what happens next. I am caring, loving, understanding and honest. Dont ask me if i have a bank account and i wont get one to help you for something. I want a real man that will love me for the rest of our lives. NO foreign people please. No Scammers whatsoever. I am sick of these fake people asking for money. And dont ask to use my cell phone number for something. I wont give it out.
